Ciindi naakali muntolongo ku Egepita , sena Josefa wakalizyi kuti wakali kuyoobikkwa kuba mweendelezi wabili mu Egepita naa kuti wakali kuyoobelesyegwa a Jehova ikufwutula mukwasyi wakwe kunzala ?
Mucikozyanyo eeci , Jesu waamba nkamu zyobilo , nkamu yambelele alimwi ayampongo .
Ibunji bwabapainiya balakonzya kuluula zyakabacitikila zikozyanya azeezi .
Weelede kuziba kuti luyando lwesu ndwakumugwasya kuti amuzibe kabotu Mulengi wakwe , aswene afwaafwi kuli Nguwe , akugwasigwa abusolozi Bwakwe .
Ambweni inga mwawayawaya kwaamba boobu kuli simweenda nzila naa kumuntu ngomutazyibene kabotu .
Lugwalo lwa 1 Johane 5 : 3 lwaamba kuti : “ Oku nkokuyanda Leza , kuti twabamba milazyo yakwe , alimwi milazyo yakwe tiili miyumu . ”
Muciindi caboobo , kwiinda mukukwabililwa a Jehova , nkamu yoonse yakazabuka .
Mpoonya wakamanizya ulaamba : “ Nkaambo kaako mutayoowi , mulayandika kwiinda tuyuni tunji . ”
Kubusena oobu kwakali kulamfwu , Davida wakabona kuti wakanyina mulongwe wakali kukonzya kumukwabilila .
Bbaibbele kunyina nolyaamba cacigaminina kujatikizya makani aakubusyigwa kwabana ibakaindilila naa bakafwa akaambo kakutulubanya .
Mu August 25 , 2004 , bakwesu bakalomba wakali muleli wacisi ca Russia Vladimir Putin ku Kremlin .
Ino mukanzide kucita nzi kujatikizya Bwami ?
Nkakaambo kaako Ijwi lya Leza ncoliti : “ Mutwe uuli amvwi munsini wabulemu , ulajanwa munzila yabululami ! ” — Tus .
